### Test 1: A speeding vehicle (Should get a fine)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/traffic/check
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "vehicleId": "MH12AB1234",
  "speed": 105.0,
  "zone": "Pune-West",
  "emergencyVehicle": false
}

### Test 2: A safe driver
POST http://localhost:8080/api/traffic/check
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "vehicleId": "MH14XY5678",
  "speed": 65.0,
  "zone": "Pune-East",
