}

### Test 3: An ambulance speeding (Should be ignored)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/traffic/check
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "vehicleId": "AMB-9999",
  "speed": 130.0,
  "zone": "Mumbai",
  "emergencyVehicle": true
}